runs.comm: swings it back in and he tucks it away wide of square leg

timber! Tamim doesn't know what's hit him! Vitori's broken the middle stump as well, the ball nipped back in and skidded through, Tamim was forward to defend and was bowled through the gate, the top part of the middle stump is chipped off and goes flying
clips a low full toss straight to mid-on
fullish on middle and off and he works it towards mid-on
hits the body and rolls to the on side and Utseya attacks the ball and underarms it towards the stumps, misses
fullish in length outside off and he drives it towards cover
very streaky! Shakib gave him the charge and made room too, goes for the slash and gets an outside edge that flies over the keeper and slip
repeats the shot he was trying the previous ball, made room, down the track and cut wide of point, was well in control of this
this was short too and Shakib pulls and doesn't time it as well, down to deep midwicket
fullish swinging on the pads and he works it to deep midwicket
wasn't in control of that shot at all, wanted to pull but got an inside edge to the pads
Shakib wants to swing at everything, swings at thin air and the ball just clears the middle stump
this one angles away from him, tries to cut but misses
stays back and he pushes it back to the bowler
tucks him up for room, he ends up chopping it towards the off side, decides against the single
Vitoru errs by bowling it full and wide outside off, too wide, he bends down and drives hard past cover
tucked him up for room but Shamsur did well by gently knocking it to the off side for a single
that's a poor delivery by Vitori, this was short and wide outside the off stump and slashed well over point
lands it on middle and off, cramped for room and he works it to the off side
played with soft hands to the on side and sets off quickly, bowler comes in Shakib's way but no harm done
makes a lot of room and he punches it to the off side
he comes round the wicket and bowls it far too wide outside off, too full as well and he stays beside the line and drives wide of point
Shakib gives him the charge and lofts him cleanly over the covers, packed off side field
fires that flat and he works it to the on side
skids it through and he's beaten on the drive
Taylor's missed a stumping! Utseya tossed it up, Shamsur was down the pitch and squared up, Taylor failed to pouch it, the batsman was well out of the crease
fires that down the leg side, clips the keeper and they take another run
steers it to the off side
makes room and drills a low full toss to long-on
starts off with a front foot no-ball, he makes room and punches it towards cover and they take a quick single
Free Hit and it's a dot ball! This was full and in the length to drive, he only placed it straight to cover
this was short and he stays at the crease and pulls him over deep midwicket, clean strike
Shakib's looking dangerous! This was fuller outside off and he reaches out and scoops it over extra cover
places it straight to mid-off
this is a low full toss and he slams it straight to midwicket
finds the gap this time, this was full on the pads and he clips it away wide of midwicket and well fielded
goes back, waits for the turn and punches it to the off side
beaten in turn and flight, tossed up outside off, wanted to crash it through the off side, misses it
fires that full outside off and he drives to cover
full outside the off stump and pushed straight to mid-off
on the pads and worked to the on side
flatter and fuller and drive down to long-off, brings up the fifty stand
tossed up outside the off stump and driven down to deep extra cover
tossed up on the pads and clipped away to midwicket
this was dropped short and he mistimes the pull to long-on
another short ball and he stays at the crease and pulls him down to deep square leg
makes room and he aims to carve it towards cover but instead mistimes it to the on side, played too early
clips it towards deep midwicket
stays back and he knocks it towards long-on
that should help his strike rate! A friendly full toss to break the shackles, he clubs it high over deep midwicket
he drops it short and he stays back and pulls it to long-on
he errs by bowling a fuller delivery on the pads and he swings it towards deep midwicket, Shamsur opening up here
he goes over the off side this time! Makes room and smashes it over extra cover
stays back and pushes it to the off side
he makes room and tries to steer it away but ends up hitting it back to the bowler
down the leg side and he places it wide of short fine leg who gives chase but can't pull it back
this was dropped a fraction short and Shakib mistimed it towards long-on, could have carried all the way to the fielder
worked away to the on side, he tries to sweep
Shakib gets a leading edge that pops over point
works it away towards square leg
fullish in length on middle and leg and he clears the back leg and mows it to long-on
Shamsur really has his eye now alright! Excellent improvisation, gets on his knee and scoops him over short fine leg
slower ball outside off and he punches it to point
bowls that fuller and he tries to dig it out, places it back to the bowler
he makes room this time and he chips a low full toss over point
almost carried all the way! Shamsur moved across the stumps and scooped a low full toss over short fine leg
full on the pads and clipped straight to midwicket
bang! Panyangara errs by pitching it up outside off with Shakib giving room, bashes it hard and the ball races away wide of mid-off
swings and fails to out away another fuller one, Shakib is frustrated with himself as the ball rolls to the on side
fullish and wide outside off and he pushes it towards mid-off
good length drifting on the body and he pulls him down to fine leg
bangs it in short and it's a sharp bouncer that fizzes past his face

they'e missed a run-out opportunity! Shamsur tries to work it to the on side but the ball clips his pad and lobs up, Vitori charges forward, so does Shakib who sets off for a run that was never there, he turns back and Vitori takes aim at his end and the throw is so wide that even the fielder at the stumps couldn't stop it
steers it to the off side, another dot ball
bowls him a bouncer and he swivels and tries to pull, the ball lands towards square leg
sweeps him towards deep square leg and he picks up a couple to bring up his fifty
tossed up and Shakib clears the back leg and heaves it over the long-on rope, the fielder made a brave attempt at catching that
full and wide outside off and he digs it out to the off side
tossed up outside the off stump he lofts it just over the bowler's head
another six just clears the rope! Shakib gives the charge and lofts towards deep midwicket, Raza tries to catch it but can't get his hand to it
flatter and shorter and he punches it towards point
Taylor's missed yet another stumping! How costly is this? Shakib is down the track and he swings and misses, Taylor fails to glove it again, poor Utseya, how unlucky is he?
is there something here? A ball after getting a life Shakib tries to slog this one out of the ground, doesn't get the distance and Waller takes it
tossed up and he gets on his knee and sweeps to deep square leg, brings up his fifty

are Bangladesh losing the plot here? Yet another slog sweep that doesn't come off, this time it's a top edge and Taylor makes amends for his stumping miss and takes the catch, nearly collides with another fielder
tossed up slowly, he makes room and cuts towards point

appeal for a run-out! He gets a leading edge towards long-off, they take the first run and then set off for the second, flat throw from Raza and Nasir is just short as the bowler gathers the ball and breaks the stumps
full outside off and driven wide of cover
drops it short and he rocks back and bashes it wide of cover
full outside the off stump and driven straight to long-off
works it towards short fine leg

and we have yet another run out in the same over would you believe it! Mushfiqur pushed it wide of the bowler on the off side and set off for a risky single, Mutombodzi attacked the ball and fired it to the keeper, Mahmudullah was struggling and well short
this was short and wide outside off and he bashes it down to deep cover, confusion in the calling there
this was drifting down the leg side
nearly finds the edge! This one skidded through and Zia fished at that
beaten again! This was a better ball, closer to the off stump, moved in and then the other way, Zia nearly edge that
the pressure gets to the batsman as he gives the charge and swings wildly, and yes he missed it again
and he finally gets some bat on it this time but it's an outside edge to third man
and the captain relieves the pressure with a six! This was short and he swivels and pulls over deep midwicket, a charged up captain yells at Zia
and we have a collision! Drills the ball to long-on and the batsmen collide midway, all happening here, luckily for it doesn't cost the visitors
he fires a yorker length delivery outside off and drills it to cover
and yet another wicket falls! Ziaur was udner pressure to score, he chips down the track and lofts him straight to deep extra cover

do we have yet another run out?? Tough one for the third umpire. Mushfiqur slogs the ball to wide long-on, they take the first run and set off for the second, the throw is flat and to the keeper, Mushfiqur dives and Taylor breaks the stumps, the bat bounced up and appeared to be in the air when the bails were dislodged, the third umpire is taking his time. He studies countless replays and he isn't 100% certain the bat was grounded properly and he rules in favour of the batsman!
full outside the off stump and he gets down and bashes it away to long-off, a boundary to relieve the pressure
short and wide outside the off stump and he hops at the crease and punches it to the off side
Mushfiqur's turning it on! This was full and wide outside the off stump and he reaches forward and scoops it over extra cover
swings across the line and he places it to deep midwicket
this was short and fizzing towards the face and he swings and misses
Gazi tries to paddle scoop it and he gets an inside edge clips his pads and rolls to the off side, they sneak a single
he shuffles and chips it over square leg and Gazi thinks of two but the captain's happy with one! He wants the strike
the captain wanted the strike and he's out off the first ball! It was a low full toss, Mushfiqur went across and tried to smash that over deep square leg, Williams takes it well in front of the rope
he moves across his stumps and tries the lap shot! The ball only clips his pads and rolls away, only a single
no he can't! This was full and a touch wide outside off, Razzak made a bit of room, failed to make contact
keeps it tight again! This was another fuller delivery, on the stumps, swings and mistimes the hoick to the deep on the on side
excellent over this from Panyangara! Razzak swings again at a full delivery outside off, no contact, Taylor jumps up in celebration knowing they have this in the bag
and a wicket to finish things off! Panyangara continues bowling it full, on the stumps, swings and the ball hits the pads, plumb in front, what a terrific last over that was by Panyangara
